✅ **Always validate input** - Never trust user input  
✅ **Use security middleware** - Helmet protects against common attacks  
✅ **Implement rate limiting** - Prevents DoS attacks  
✅ **Handle errors gracefully** - Don't expose sensitive details in production  
✅ **Sanitize responses** - Ensure data type safety  
✅ **Use environment variables** - Never hardcode configuration  

