| No input validation | Added parameter validation with bounds checking |
| Unhandled errors | Added global error handler middleware |
| No payload limit | Set JSON payload limit to 10KB |
| No request timeout | Added 30-second request timeout |
| Error info leakage | Conditionally hide error details in production |
| No pagination | Added limit/offset parameters with validation |
| Unvalidated query params | Coerce and validate numeric parameters |

